# ### 17  NO "Simplified / Stand‑alone / Partial / Backup" Clones

* Never commit files named `*-simplified.*`, `*-fixed.*`, `*-standalone.*`, `*-partial.*`, `*-fragment.*`, `*-backup.*`.
* Experiment in `/tmp/` or a throw‑away branch, port fixes to the real file, delete scratch copies.
